{"tid":900990,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"葡國菜食評 - BOM Cuisine","createTime":"2018-11-13T16:04:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-15T11:28:09.000Z","uid":175988,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6a7f4e86b43515a0ccda3e324a58cff1985179d3","tid":900990,"uid":175988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T16:04:16.000Z","msg":"<strong>BOM Cuisine @ 長沙灣</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/VogL9pr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FVogL9pr.jpg&h=66e592ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>葡萄牙烤乳豬伴黃薑飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n乳豬皮脆肉香，食落油脂豐潤，肉質腍滑，略嫌脂肪比例太多<br />\n紅酒汁帶淡淡甘甜，同濃味嘅乳豬非常撘配，解膩之餘仲提升咗味道層次<br />\n用熱鐵板上菜，保持食物溫度<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香料味道唔太突出，主要食肉嘅䶢香<br />\n黃薑飯普普通通，飯上面嘅配料味道特別，唔識欣賞<br />\n<br />\n<strong>結論:$108包餐湯+沙律+主菜+甜品+飲品+服務費，咁嘅質素算係抵屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong>"},{"pid":"cb01e8e5d2911c522951e285e141e0b5de35c32f","tid":900990,"uid":175988,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T00:31:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"767ead2e2bc75d4c037e8f73dea1144271ea5600","tid":900990,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T01:32:28.000Z","msg":"太貴<br />\n$50差唔多"},{"pid":"94fa9e5d507e32c82655189be30dfc406387d3e5","tid":900990,"uid":9387,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"767ead2e2bc75d4c037e8f73dea1144271ea5600","tid":900990,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T01:32:28.000Z","msg":"太貴<br />\n$50差唔多"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T01:53:11.000Z","msg":"50蚊食燒肉飯就夠"},{"pid":"c4cbe6626ab220770e74da8d6eafcfec0289f00d","tid":900990,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pi